#include<cstdio>
#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
    int x1,y1,x2,y2,x3,y3,x4,y4,tc;
    scanf("%d",&tc);
    while(tc--)
    {
       scanf("%d %d %d %d",&x1,&y1,&x2,&y2);    
       scanf("%d %d %d %d",&x3,&y3,&x4,&y4);   
       if(x3>x2||y3>y2||x1>x4||y1>y4)
       {
          printf("No Overlap\n");
          continue;                             
       }
       else
       {
         printf("%d ",x3>x1?x3:x1);
         printf("%d ",y3>y1?y3:y1);
         printf("%d ",x4>x2?x2:x4);
         printf("%d\n",y4>y2?y2:y4);
       }
           
               
    }
    
    
    
return 0;    
}
